@startuml
title TPL Architecture - Container View

left to right direction
skinparam shadowing false

rectangle "Frontend (React + Vite)\nfrontend/src/**" as FE
rectangle "Backend API (FastAPI)\nbackend/app/routers/**" as API
rectangle "Backend Features (Services)\nbackend/app/features/**" as SVC
rectangle "Domain Model (SQLAlchemy)\nbackend/app/model/**" as MODEL
database "Database\nSQLite/Postgres-compatible" as DB
rectangle "Spec Tooling\nqa/spec_tools/**" as QA
folder "Specifications\nspec/**" as SPEC

FE --> API : JSON/HTTP
API --> SVC : orchestrates use-cases
SVC --> MODEL : domain + persistence operations
MODEL --> DB : ORM mapping
QA --> SPEC : reads spec artifacts
QA --> MODEL : introspects SQLAlchemy metadata
QA --> API : optional spec-driven runtime checks

@enduml
